==Latin==

===Verb===
{{latinverb|[[possum]]|posse|potu&#299;}}

# be [[able]], [[can]]

===Usage===
;[[Tunc]], [[modo]] [[edere]] potuit.:At that time, he just could not eat.
;Possum [[latine]] [[loqui]].: I can speak Latin.
;Potes[[ne]] [[mihi]] [[succurrere]],[[quaeso]]?:Can you help me please?


